<section class="py-20 md:py-32 border-t border-border/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
          Agent memory was never built.<br />
          <span class="text-muted">It was stitched together.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Your agent's memory is 4 services, 2,000 lines of glue, and a prayer.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          One retrieval mode. No decay. No consolidation. No causal reasoning.
          No temporal recall. No analogy. Just similarity search and hope.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm border-l-2 border-accent/40 pl-4">
          This isn't a feature gap. It's an architectural ceiling. An LLM call per write costs 200–2000ms. A network hop to an external vector DB costs 2–20ms per read. No crash safety. No atomicity. These constraints are baked into the stack. You can't fix them without rewriting the storage layer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface/40 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-mono text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">The status quo</p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm space-y-1.5">
            <p class="text-red">Postgres</p>
            <p class="text-red">+ Qdrant</p>
            <p class="text-red">+ Redis</p>
            <p class="text-red">+ Neo4j</p>
            <p class="text-red">+ 2,000 lines of glue</p>
            <div class="border-t border-border my-3"></div>
            <p class="text-muted">4 services. <span class="text-red font-medium">50–200ms.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-accent/30 bg-accent/[0.04] p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-mono text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">HEBBS</p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm space-y-1.5">
            <p class="text-accent">hebbs-server</p>
            <div class="border-t border-accent/20 my-3"></div>
            <p class="text-muted">1 binary. <span class="text-accent font-medium">&lt;10ms.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
